name: Anne
description:
Horror Facts Story No. 02

Last mercy is no mercy. This artwork is made to remind us about Anna Boleyn, The first British Queen, first woman who has high society class that has to be consort to be publicly beheaded. 

The horror fact is, our head remain conscious after being decapitated. We still can see and understand public emotions of our death before our body is shutted down forever. That's why the eyes of beheaded people in the movie remain open.

3500 x 5000 px
